{"tid":1164324,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"講一講香港司法同大陸司法有咩唔同?","createTime":"2019-05-21T03:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T13:51:32.000Z","uid":193217,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c92401cc56502ddacaaac75cd71fe713f1438a6a","tid":1164324,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T03:49:09.000Z","msg":"香港司法:係無罪推定.即係你就算上到庭你都仲係清白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後再用證據定明你係有罪<br />\n<br />\n而大陸既司法:係有罪判定.即係你一上到庭你就已經係有罪<br />\n極端到你未到司法機構判已經話你有罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後再用證據去洗脫自己無罪<br />\n<br />\n2者有咩唔同呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n據今天公布的中國最高法院的年度工作報告內容，2015年，中國法院起訴的案件中，幾乎100％的被告被認定有罪，法新社報道注意到，這一情況是在北京承諾減少冤假錯案的數量之後。報道指出， 中國司法體系名聲不好，被指濫用職權，特別是警察和國安刑訊逼供。人權組織指責中國司法是在黨的領導監督下的司法程序，所有的維權活動人士都被會認定有罪。<br />\n<br />\n據報告，2015年，有1039人被中國的法院&ldquo;發現無辜&rdquo;，不過，有1232000名被告被定罪，定罪率達99.92％。在 2014年，778人被認定無罪或釋放，而1184000人被判刑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我預祝支持過既港豬準備某年某月比人用100%既認罪率黎搭上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d458293b3e4781f5dbc053f1a4a6247f47d5eec5","tid":1164324,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T13:45:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c0b9d5df2fae9ef03e18381f5d521b5a731205d","tid":1164324,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T13:51:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Lmi5tTLI5x4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLmi5tTLI5x4&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbf%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=54815516\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Lmi5tTLI5x4</a><br />\n事先聲明.段片係殘體字<br />\n但佢講到大陸司法到底係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你比佢引渡比死更難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}